# ── Internal planning docs (not for public repo) ────────────────────────────────
# Roadmaps/upgrade plans live here for internal use only. User-facing docs
# (Phase 10 "Docs tab" content, API reference, quickstart) must NOT live under
# this folder — put those under a committed path (e.g. /website, /public-docs)
# so they aren't accidentally hidden from the OSS repo.
docs/

